+---
+description: Low-cost contract compatibility check for bounded Redis, DTO, WebSocket, REST, or DB changes in the trade project
+---
+
+When the user types `/trade-fast-contract-check <scope>`, do a bounded compatibility review first.
+
+## Model lane
+Use **Gemini Flash + Fast** by default.
+
+## Mission
+Validate `<scope>` for local compatibility with minimal token usage.
+
+## Execution sequence
+1. Act as **@trade-lead** and list changed producers, consumers, and schemas.
+2. Load **trade-project-core** and **trade-contract-regression**.
+3. Produce:
+   - current contract
+   - proposed contract
+   - field-level diff
+   - compatibility verdict
+   - required fixture/tests
+
+## Escalate to premium if
+- breaking compatibility is possible
+- migration/deprecation sequencing is non-trivial
+- more than 2 transport/storage boundaries change together
